# The test file for en_us text normalisation
# The format of a test is:
# NAME ||| TESTSENT ||| CORRECTSENT ||| SHOULDFAIL
# NAME = The name of the test. E.g. digit1. Does not have to be unique but it helps for debugging.
# TESTSENT = The sentence containing the test case.
# CORRECTSENT = The sentence which should be output by the normaliser.
# SHOULDFAIL = If 0 we expect this test to be succesfull. If 1 we expect it not to be and that's ok.
